        "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-2efe91 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-84d389 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-8d9407 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-e3b0c4\"><p class=\"level1\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000145\">第一章 “演员”越来越清晰，“剧本”越来越模糊</$link></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-2efe91 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-84d389 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-8d9407 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-e3b0c4\"><p class=\"level2\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000147\">辛亥革命“成功”了吗？</$link></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-2efe91 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-84d389 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-8d9407 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-e3b0c4\"><p class=\"level2\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000153\">“辛亥观”的演变</$link></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-2efe91 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-84d389 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-8d9407 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-e3b0c4\"><p class=\"level2\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000158\">“细节化”的辛亥叙事：什么是“政党”</$link></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-2efe91 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-84d389 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-8d9407 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-e3b0c4\"><p class=\"level2\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000163\">革命还是立宪：也许是个假问题？</$link></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-2efe91 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-84d389 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-8d9407 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-e3b0c4\"><p class=\"level2\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000172\">“政治革命”还是“种族革命”</$link></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-2efe91 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-84d389 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-8d9407 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-e3b0c4\"><p class=\"level2\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000175\">和平的君主立宪可能吗？不可能仅仅因为是满族皇帝？</$link></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-2efe91 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-84d389 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-8d9407 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-e3b0c4\"><p class=\"level2\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000181\">辛亥研究，如今细节是越来越清楚，背景却越来越模糊了</$link></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-2efe91 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-84d389 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-8d9407 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-e3b0c4\"><p class=\"level1\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000188\">第二章 “改朝换代”与君主和平立宪的可能性问题—— “封建”与帝制的比较</$link></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-2efe91 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-84d389 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-8d9407 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-e3b0c4\"><p class=\"level2\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000190\">假如辛亥前是汉族王朝？</$link></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-2efe91 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-84d389 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-8d9407 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-e3b0c4\"><p class=\"level2\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000200\">辛亥革命推翻了什么“王朝”？论此王朝并非彼“王朝”（dynasty）</$link></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-2efe91 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-84d389 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-8d9407 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-e3b0c4\"><p class=\"level2\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000208\">“光荣的女王” 是个“亡国之君”？</$link></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-2efe91 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-84d389 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-8d9407 twpub-d2a9d2644ad14f76-e3b0c4\"><p class=\"level2\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d2a9d2644ad14f76/text/000000215\">“有国王的共和国”与“半封建”帝国的宪政之路</$link></p></div>"
        },
